option.value: How to convert inches to meters?

option.name: content
option.value:
To convert inches to meters, you can use the conversion factor of 0.0254 meters per inch.
Multiply the number of inches you have by 0.0254 to get the equivalent measurement in meters.
For example, if you have 10 inches:
10 inches * 0.0254 meters/inch = 0.254 meters
So, 10 inches is equal to 0.254 meters.
